name: 甘奈
text: おはよーございまーす
trans: Good morning.

name: 甜花
text: おはよう……ございます……
trans: Good morning... Na-chan... thank you for coming with Tenka along early...

name: 甜花
text: なーちゃん……一緒に早く来てくれて、ありがと……
trans: No, it's alright! Besides, I have this magazine that I so wanted to read!

name: 甘奈
text:
ううん、全然いいよー！　読みたい雑誌あったし！
じゃあ甜花ちゃん、レッスンがんばってね！
trans:
Well, Tenka,
hope you do well in your lessons!

name: 甜花
text: うん……がんばって、くる……
trans: Yes... Tenka will do her best...

name: 甘奈
text: いってらっしゃーい！
trans: Have fun there!

name: 甘奈
text: 何から読もっかなー☆
trans: I wonder which I should read...

name: 甘奈
text: あれ？　なんだろう、この箱とメモ……？
trans: Hmm? What's this box and note?

name: 甘奈
text:
『社長からの差し入れです
みなさんでどうぞ　はづき』……
trans:
"This is from the President,
please help yourself to one. -Hazuki"

name: 甘奈
text:
わぁー、プリンだ！
しかもこれ、並ばないと買えないって評判のやつ！
trans: Wow, it's creme caramel! Not to mention, this one's very popular that you can't buy it without having to wait!

name: 甘奈
text:
さっすが社長さん、
イマドキの女の子の流行りをわかってるー☆
trans:
That is so like the President,
knowing what's in with the girls today.

name: 甘奈
text:
（……あれ？
でも、もうひとつしか残ってないや）
trans:
(Wait...
There's only one here remaining.)

name: 甘奈
text:
（じゃあ、甜花ちゃんに取っといてあげよっと
甜花ちゃん、プリン好きだもんね☆）
trans: (In that case, I'll save this for Tenka since she loves creme caramel.)

name: 甘奈
text:
甜花ちゃんにメモ残しとこっと☆
喜んでくれるといいなぁ
trans:
I'll leave a note for Tenka,
I hope that she'll be happy about this.

name: 甜花
text: あぅ……レッスン、つかれた……
trans: Awh... Tenka's so tired from the lesson...

name: 甜花
text: （あれ……このメモ、なんだろ……？）
trans: (Hmm? What is this note?)

name: 甜花
text: 『冷蔵庫にプリンあるよ☆　甘奈』……
trans: There's a creme caramel for you at the refrigerator -Amana

name: 甜花
text: わぁ……プリン……！
trans: Aah, a creme caramel!

name: 甜花
text:
あ……このプリン……
なーちゃんの雑誌で見たやつ……
trans:
Ah... This creme caramel...
It's the same one that Na-chan's looking at the magazine...

name: 甜花
text: にへへ……美味しそう……
trans: Nihehe, It looks delicious...

name: 甜花
text:
あ、でも……１個しかない……
なーちゃんの分は……？
trans: Wait there's only one here... Where's Na-chan's sharing? Maybe Na-chan already ate hers?

name: 甜花
text:
もう、食べたのかな……？
甜花、食べても……いい……？
trans:
It's okay for Tenka to eat this... right?
......Tenka will save it for later...

name: 甜花
text: ……やっぱり、やめよう……
trans: I guess not...

name: 甘奈
text: ただいまー☆
trans: I'm back.

name: 甘奈
text: はー、お腹ぺっこぺこだよ～
trans: Aah, I'm so hungry.

name: 甘奈
text:
（あのプリン……
やっぱ、ちょっと食べたかったかなー？）
trans:
(That creme caramel...
I guess I kinda wanted to have some taste of it.)

name: 甘奈
text:
あ、甜花ちゃん！
待っててくれたの？
trans:
Oh, Tenka!
Were you waiting for me?

name: 甜花
text: うん……なーちゃん、待ってた……
trans: Yes... Yes, Tenka did...

name: 甜花
text:
あの、なーちゃん……
こっち、来て……
trans:
Umm, Na-chan...
Please come here...

name: 甘奈
text: 冷蔵庫……？
trans: At the refrigerator?

name: 甘奈
text: あっ、プリン残ってる！
trans: Ah, the creme caramel's still there!

name: 甘奈
text:
あっれー！？　甜花ちゃんプリン食べなかったの？
こーゆう本格的なの苦手だったっけ？
trans:
Wait! You didn't want to eat this, Tenka?
You don't like full-blown thing like this?

name: 甜花
text:
ううん、好き……でも……
甜花……なーちゃんと、食べたくて……
trans:
No, Tenka does like it... but...
Tenka wants to... eat it with you, Na-chan...

name: 甘奈
text:
甜花ちゃん……！
えへへ、じゃあふたりとも同じこと考えてたんだね
trans:
Tenka!
Ehehe, looks like we were thinking of the same thing.

name: 甜花
text: にへへ……そうだね……
trans: Nihehe...  I guess so...

name: 甘奈・甜花
text: じゃあ
trans: In that case,

name: 甜花
text: ふたりで
trans: We should...

name: 甘奈
text: 半分こしよ☆
trans: Share this between us!
